text: At Gunpoint is a 1955 American western movie directed by Alfred L. Werker and starring Fred MacMurray, Dorothy Malone, Walter Brennan, Skip Homeier, Tommy Rettig, John Qualen. It was distributed by Allied Artists Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1955 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Alfred L.
